{"tid":1552930,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"超級感動！！！好多人唱《我願榮光歸香港》","createTime":"2019-09-08T12:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T18:28:17.000Z","uid":274371,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a547c70571aa0f47c3f0d1dbb07deebe36d5ab60","tid":1552930,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:36:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日聽到有人拎住個藍芽喇叭一播，好多附近嘅人都即刻識跟住唱，有人喺現場派歌詞同Airdrop歌詞畀身邊嘅人<br />\n<br />\n相信好快好多香港人都會識呢首歌，每次出嚟都唱，喺街上面又唱，夜晚十點又唱，諗起都開心🇭🇰<br />\n<br />\n喺呢到好想多謝參與製作呢首歌嘅巴絲，你哋畀咗一個盛載身份認同嘅器皿我哋，凝聚各路人馬。歷史定必記載你哋嘅付出！！！</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"e0d33c30b752f6aa6f5579118cb4f63ce12ef082","tid":1552930,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:36:56.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"45f23b0956402fd5e1f8bd591be5ec5aac2d6114","tid":1552930,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:37:06.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1fbb13e16e42bddcb281b69d9156c1c9670b1a47","tid":1552930,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"21ee5b71914724448f3b827cdfcd77a530766e41","tid":1552930,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"354b533042282c2f41960a2a4e4e014bba02b262","tid":1552930,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:37:50.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"4a1da5f5ba77c35d5f7e7e07c5f56ba9aa6e4ff3","tid":1552930,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"00af03ddb6ee2ab48378b91b6b5368ef98b